         <div type="translation" resp="#jmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p>To the Genius of the colony, Septimia Lepcis Magna, the fortunate. By decree of the most splendid city-council.</p></div>
         
         <div type="translation" source="#tantillo2010" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Al Genio della colonia Septimia di Leptis Magna, felice, per decreto dell’ordine splendidissimo.</p></div>
         
         <div type="translation" source="#lsa" xml:lang="en">
            <p>To the Genius of the fortunate colony Septimia of Lepcis Magna, by decree of the most splendid council (<foreign xml:lang="la">ordo</foreign>) [this was set up].</p>
         </div>
